casebody.data:
Edward G. McDONOUGH, petitioner,
v.
Youel SMITH, Individually and as Special District Attorney for the County of Rensselaer, New York, aka Trey Smith. No. 18-485. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 11, 2019.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit granted.
